Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Head MRI
When I select 'Hearing impairment' from 'Previous interventions/therapies' dropdown menu
Then 'Add clinic' button is enabled
And 'Hearing loss' checkbox is enabled
And 'Hyperacusis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Hypoacusis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tinnitus' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sensorineural hearing loss' checkbox is enabled

And 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Hypoacusis' checkbox
Then 'Conductive hearing loss' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sensorineural hearing loss' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Tinnitus' checkbox
Then 'Pulsatile' checkbox is enabled
